fields.question: What payment methods do you accept?
fields.answer: We accept all major credit and debit cards, including Visa, MasterCard, and American Express. We also offer the option to pay via PayPal for added convenience.

fields.question: Can I return or exchange an item?
fields.answer: Yes, you can return or exchange an item within 30 days of purchase. Please ensure that the item is in its original packaging and has not been used. For more information, please refer to our Returns & Exchanges policy.

fields.question: How can I contact customer support?
fields.answer: You can contact our customer support team by emailing  info@Shop-Genius.com or by calling our toll-free number at 1-800-123-4567. Our team is available to assist you with any questions or concerns you may have.

fields.question: Are all products on your website authentic?
fields.answer: Yes, we guarantee that all products on our website are 100% authentic. We work directly with authorized distributors and manufacturers to ensure the quality and authenticity of every product we sell.

fields.question: How can I reset my password?
fields.answer: You can reset your password by clicking on the "Forgot Password" link on the login page. You will be prompted to enter your email address, and a password reset link will be sent to your inbox. Follow the instructions in the email to reset your password.
